  "detailed_description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >No Pressure: Hive War</h2></strong><br><br>Experience a challenging and fun top-down space shooter. Play as the sole survivor of the Human Alliance Federation's space fleet, battling the menacing hive. Defeat the Hive Ship to save the planet and compete on the leaderboard for an exciting and nostalgic adventure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645650/extras/a8474ed71cfee48d92179aef31cdd151.poster.avif?t=1724104617\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645650/extras/a8474ed71cfee48d92179aef31cdd151.webm?t=1724104617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645650/extras/a8474ed71cfee48d92179aef31cdd151.mp4?t=1724104617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Warping</h2>Boasting our Top of the range never seen before warp technology:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645650/extras/dbdfac05ab6cc5945bd8e615a201a7c6.poster.avif?t=1724104617\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645650/extras/dbdfac05ab6cc5945bd8e615a201a7c6.webm?t=1724104617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645650/extras/dbdfac05ab6cc5945bd8e615a201a7c6.mp4?t=1724104617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Leaderboard</h2>Compete against others on the global stage through the Leaderboard:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645650/extras/27df4e4f5a62b91b1767e0f9b8897512.poster.avif?t=1724104617\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645650/extras/27df4e4f5a62b91b1767e0f9b8897512.webm?t=1724104617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645650/extras/27df4e4f5a62b91b1767e0f9b8897512.mp4?t=1724104617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Reflex</h2>Use your superior pilot reflexes to avoid the hazards and gain the upper hand in a tight situation:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645650/extras/b79f20a9af7e1aff7322f7fb210a10f1.poster.avif?t=1724104617\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645650/extras/b79f20a9af7e1aff7322f7fb210a10f1.webm?t=1724104617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645650/extras/b79f20a9af7e1aff7322f7fb210a10f1.mp4?t=1724104617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Frigate</h2>Defeat the frigates every 5 waves to earn upgrade points for your ship:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645650/extras/fc2716c46bb54f2abe75ae8635ecdfd9.poster.avif?t=1724104617\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645650/extras/fc2716c46bb54f2abe75ae8635ecdfd9.webm?t=1724104617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645650/extras/fc2716c46bb54f2abe75ae8635ecdfd9.mp4?t=1724104617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weapons</h2>Upgrade your Ship and Weapons to hit harder and survive longer.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645650/extras/b81e3aa6b97b3b506752b47c82348ebc.poster.avif?t=1724104617\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645650/extras/b81e3aa6b97b3b506752b47c82348ebc.webm?t=1724104617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645650/extras/b81e3aa6b97b3b506752b47c82348ebc.mp4?t=1724104617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ship Unlocks</h2>​Defeat the game to earn new ship unlocks.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645650/extras/9720a8dc9d8ea47ea47bbfacbcbfc416.poster.avif?t=1724104617\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645650/extras/9720a8dc9d8ea47ea47bbfacbcbfc416.webm?t=1724104617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645650/extras/9720a8dc9d8ea47ea47bbfacbcbfc416.mp4?t=1724104617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defeat the Hiveship</h2>Fight valiantly through the seemingly endless waves to reach and defeat the Hive Ship to truly prove your worth and earn new shipunlocks.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645650/extras/049831989b1356f700250e53ee01d649.poster.avif?t=1724104617\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645650/extras/049831989b1356f700250e53ee01d649.webm?t=1724104617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://s